data.description: Step into a serene 3BR, 2BA oasis in Quailwood's peaceful cul-de-sac. This 1,829 sqft home sits on a substantial 8,699 sqft lot, surrounded by mature trees. Featuring high vaulted ceilings, a welcoming fireplace, and a spacious living area, the residence exudes comfort. A newly updated kitchen shines with granite countertops and sophisticated cabinetry. The master suite is a luxurious retreat with a custom-tiled jetted tub. The backyard paradise offers a pool, landscaped garden, and evening-lit walkways. Ready for the next chapter of your story? Reach out to turn this tranquil dream into your reality.
